{"tid":1905657,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"聖水 美國女子的膀胱如釀酒廠 尿液竟然變酒","createTime":"2020-03-01T11:48:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T13:17:37.000Z","uid":32511,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e46d87dc420684db78ddd171a2fa1067e7bfe1c0","tid":1905657,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:48:00.000Z","msg":"美國醫生在醫學雜誌上披露，一名女性病患的罕見病症使其膀胱成為釀酒廠，尿液都變成酒。這是迄今已知的第一個病例。<br />\n <br />\n美國內科醫師學會出版的學術醫學雜誌《內科學年刊》（Annals of Internal Medicine）刊登的一篇報告指出，匹茲堡大學醫學中心（University of Pittsburgh Medical<br />\nCenter）的醫生在檢驗一名61歲女性病患時發現，她的尿液竟然變成酒。<br />\n <br />\n該名女子因罹患肝硬化和糖尿病，需要進行肝臟移植，醫生先替她進行檢驗，以決定其移植的順位。<br />\n <br />\n儘管該名女子聲稱，她從不碰酒，但醫生一開始不太相信，因為她的尿液對酒精的檢測結果一直都呈現陽性，但她還是堅持說，她不喝酒。<br />\n <br />\n後來，有些臨床醫生注意到，她的尿檢結果對於乙基葡萄糖醛酸苷（ethyl glucuronide）和硫酸乙酯（ethyl sulfate）等乙醇（酒精）分解而成的物質呈現陰性反應。同樣的，她的血液檢查結果對乙醇也呈現陰性。<br />\n <br />\n這意味著酒精不存在於她的血液裡，所以她沒有喝過酒或酒醉的感覺。<br />\n <br />\n基於這些奇怪的情況，該醫學中心的醫生對該名女子進行了仔細的檢查。他們發現，她的膀胱中存在一種被稱為禿髮念珠菌（Candida glabrata）的真菌，這是人體寄生菌之一，很接近啤酒酵母。<br />\n <br />\n他們將這種酵母的樣本在特定條件下置入培養皿，以觀察它是否會發酵。結果，這個樣本產出了酒精。<br />\n <br />\n釀酒廠在釀酒時需要水和糖，再加上酵母與缺氧的條件。缺氧的條件可以讓酵母將糖發酵成酒精和二氧化碳。<br />\n <br />\n而該名女子的膀胱似乎就是個釀酒廠。她因罹患糖尿病，所以尿液含糖，再加上膀胱裡的酵母，這樣的條件就適合發酵和產出酒精。<br />\n <br />\n醫生最終診斷出，該名女子罹患了「尿液自釀造症候群」（Urinary Auto-Brewery Syndrome）或「膀胱發酵症候群」（Bladder fermentation syndrome）。"},{"pid":"78a107bd5171f8d0a03200c91b3218f9bcfc2439","tid":1905657,"uid":162726,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:49:03.000Z","msg":"搓手液<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73cdfa202c89c453e88d50a15df5b517489b1de","tid":1905657,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9622c4d6f28cc06d003ed4f4d7ab30e71e121c0","tid":1905657,"uid":55511,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:49:35.000Z","msg":"屌到佢噴酒"},{"pid":"4bff8939d8f960d955a30fab5e573d8ccaa5bd3d","tid":1905657,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:49:55.000Z","msg":"如果靚女就發"},{"pid":"6a2054c7bb248f7a5953415e56c3c04d510fbf5c","tid":1905657,"uid":46587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:49:56.000Z","msg":"IG唔賣底褲有新野賣了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b905a098bb0653241cf8c5ba047ca7e75ccfdec","tid":1905657,"uid":27319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:52:48.000Z","msg":"想飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33c6cfbbcf2ad0d326a9314a7ef430c3aff95da","tid":1905657,"uid":293677,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:53:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wRiS1Nr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwRiS1Nr.jpg&h=987965a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"247019c22b6cb7c795055f4527395ea555977fe2","tid":1905657,"uid":326712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a9622c4d6f28cc06d003ed4f4d7ab30e71e121c0","tid":1905657,"uid":55511,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:49:35.000Z","msg":"屌到佢噴酒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:53:33.000Z","msg":"61歲女病患<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41019a34989f1cb10ccd1c22b45da25f423bffdd","tid":1905657,"uid":45603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bff8939d8f960d955a30fab5e573d8ccaa5bd3d","tid":1905657,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:49:55.000Z","msg":"如果靚女就發"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:53:54.000Z","msg":"呢個都靚女黎"},{"pid":"e40332df8d6a1a3e3a3611